OL,5,G1100 The Man from Laramie
OL,6,     F(1955) Classic western. James
OL,7,     FStewart plays a stranger who
OL,8,     Farrives in a remote New Mexico
OL,9,     Ftown secretly seeking his
OL,10,     Fbrother's killer. With Donald
OL,11,     FCrisp, Alex Nicol and Arthur
OL,12,     FKennedy.
OL,13,G1305 Gun Fury
OL,14,     F(1953) Western. Rock Hudson stars
OL,15,     Fas a California-bound settler who
OL,16,     Fmust ride 1500 miles to the
OL,17,     FMexican border to rescue his
OL,18,     Ffiancee (Donna Reed) after she's
OL,19,     Fabducted by an outlaw.
